Package com.Bean

Class BeanSession

java.lang.Object
com.Bean.BeanSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<BeanSession>
public class BeanSession extends Object implements Comparable<BeanSession>
Represents a user session in the application. This class encapsulates session-related details, including the session ID, user ID, and timestamps for creation, access, and expiration.

This class implements the Comparable interface to allow sorting based on the accessed time of the sessions.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Sahana
